00:44:08.910 --> 00:44:10.730
But in your case,
it was your father.

00:44:10.730 --> 00:44:12.940
In your sons' case, the
parents were the gurus.

00:44:12.940 --> 00:44:15.750
Can you talk a little bit
about having the guru live

00:44:15.750 --> 00:44:19.170
in the house itself and be
your father or your parent?

00:44:23.010 --> 00:44:26.170
SAROD MAESTRO AMJAD ALI KHAN:
It's the Indian realization

00:44:26.170 --> 00:44:33.810
of guru was much more in India.

00:44:33.810 --> 00:44:40.070
The surrendered-ness
towards God or guru

00:44:40.070 --> 00:44:44.790
was more experienced in India.

00:44:44.790 --> 00:44:49.310
And the guru demanded
complete attention,

00:44:49.310 --> 00:44:52.250
complete
surrendered-ness And most

00:44:52.250 --> 00:44:56.410
of the disciples,
the students, they

00:44:56.410 --> 00:45:02.260
worked like a domestic
help in the house.

00:45:02.260 --> 00:45:07.070
So a guru was
considered institution.

00:45:07.070 --> 00:45:12.240
Now we look for a huge
concrete building,

00:45:12.240 --> 00:45:14.630
they are called institutions.

00:45:14.630 --> 00:45:17.100
So that is the basic difference.

00:45:17.100 --> 00:45:20.820
The lifestyle changed.

00:45:20.820 --> 00:45:24.870
The requirements of
people who changed.

00:45:24.870 --> 00:45:30.270
And everybody is trying to
reach to the moon and the sun.

00:45:30.270 --> 00:45:33.680
But my father, my
guru, often said

00:45:33.680 --> 00:45:36.510
that one should be
focused in life.

00:45:36.510 --> 00:45:37.850
I can't do everything.

00:45:37.850 --> 00:45:41.310
I can't be a Ph.D. and
also play good sarod.

00:45:41.310 --> 00:45:44.010
So one has to choose right
in the beginning what

00:45:44.010 --> 00:45:46.110
you want to do with your life.

00:45:46.110 --> 00:45:51.500
And similarly, I'm sure Amaan
would like to say something.

00:45:51.500 --> 00:45:53.720
Ayaan would like
to say something.

00:45:53.720 --> 00:45:57.810
So this commitment
and realization.

00:45:57.810 --> 00:45:59.920
So we are all humble
representative

00:45:59.920 --> 00:46:04.340
of this ancient art Indian
classical music, sarod.

00:46:04.340 --> 00:46:07.900
Sarod is a Persian
word which means music.

00:46:07.900 --> 00:46:11.600
And we had great
gurus in our country.

00:46:11.600 --> 00:46:17.950
All over the world, we had great
sages, saints, philosophers.

00:46:17.950 --> 00:46:21.530
But unfortunately, nobody
could [INAUDIBLE] us.

00:46:21.530 --> 00:46:27.460
Today we have become such
a ferocious, unkind animal

00:46:27.460 --> 00:46:32.900
that the whole world is
afraid of peace, of harmony.

00:46:32.900 --> 00:46:37.190
There's a danger for world
peace and harmony in the world.

00:46:37.190 --> 00:46:39.980
So unfortunately, when
the education could not

00:46:39.980 --> 00:46:43.300
create compassion and
kindness in the human being,

00:46:43.300 --> 00:46:46.620
so we are going through
a very bad phase.

00:46:46.620 --> 00:46:53.750
And I hope people realize that
we have to share the kindness

00:46:53.750 --> 00:46:56.020
and love with our children.

00:46:56.020 --> 00:46:59.610
So we must have a-- in
our family-- as you know,

00:46:59.610 --> 00:47:03.300
my wife is Subhalakshmi--
we feel connected

00:47:03.300 --> 00:47:05.810
with every soul of the world.

00:47:05.810 --> 00:47:08.570
And we feel that we
have a common god

00:47:08.570 --> 00:47:10.850
and we are the common race.

00:47:10.850 --> 00:47:15.000
So I hope people
get this message

00:47:15.000 --> 00:47:19.560
and we are able to control
this violence and destruction

00:47:19.560 --> 00:47:22.820
for what is happening
in the world.

