realize where you're born.

00:47:43.800 --> 00:47:46.480
You just feel it's people
are looking at your parents.

00:47:46.480 --> 00:47:47.630
And oh, they are popular.

00:47:47.630 --> 00:47:48.910
You get that feeling.

00:47:48.910 --> 00:47:52.270
But as you grow up, you
realize the responsibilities

00:47:52.270 --> 00:47:53.560
that keep growing.

00:47:53.560 --> 00:47:59.120
My mother was a very eminent
Bharatanatyam dancer.

00:47:59.120 --> 00:48:02.230
She learned from Shrimati
Rukmini Devi Arundale

00:48:02.230 --> 00:48:03.950
from Chennai.

00:48:03.950 --> 00:48:07.740
