from a lineage-- well,

00:48:07.740 --> 00:48:13.100
I know where you come, but from
this heavy family of musicians.

00:48:13.100 --> 00:48:14.570
So I think it's an honor.

00:48:14.570 --> 00:48:19.210
And it is not very easy.

00:48:19.210 --> 00:48:20.240
It is difficult.

00:48:20.240 --> 00:48:22.620
But as they say, there
are no free lunches.

00:48:22.620 --> 00:48:25.280
So you enjoy all the importance,
not [INAUDIBLE] thing.

00:48:25.280 --> 00:48:27.708
So really working
hard towards that.

00:48:27.708 --> 00:48:28.583
MODERATOR: Thank you.

00:48:28.583 --> 00:48:30.489
AMAAN ALI KHAN: Ayaan.

00:48:30.489 --> 00:48:31.780
AYAAN ALI KHAN: Good afternoon.

00:48:31.780 --> 00:48:35.280
I think my brother's pretty much
covered the emotion that even

00:48:35.280 --> 00:48:36.230
I went through.

00:48:36.230 --> 00:48:41.260
But of course it was a great
honor and a great privilege

00:48:41.260 --> 00:48:46.050
also to just be born in a family
where the language spoken was

00:48:46.050 --> 00:48:46.550
music.

00:48:46.550 --> 00:48:49.110
The air we were
breathing was music.

00:48:49.110 --> 00:48:52.890
And much as I say there was
no pressure, but perhaps

00:48:52.890 --> 00:48:54.770
in a sense there always was.

00:48:54.770 --> 00:48:58.010
Because as an eight year
old or a seven year old,

00:48:58.010 --> 00:49:00.660
even when I would just go
with my father at concerts,

00:49:00.660 --> 00:49:02.162
you would meet
people who'd say, oh.

00:49:02.162 --> 00:49:04.100
We've heard your
grandfather or your father

00:49:04.100 --> 00:49:06.010
and now we are
waiting to hear you.

00:49:06.010 --> 00:49:10.610
So that, at some level, it
was all building up inside.

00:49:10.610 --> 00:49:14.950
And, of course, my parents have
been made gracious people who

00:49:14.950 --> 00:49:20.410
gave us the freedom to decide
as to whatever you want to do.

00:49:20.410 --> 00:49:26.860
But then eventually I think
we heard what the heart said.

00:49:26.860 --> 00:49:30.460
And I think it was the
right thing for us to do.

00:49:30.460 --> 00:49:33.630
And I think then we got
passionate about what

00:49:33.630 --> 00:49:35.264
we were doing.

