AYAAN ALI KHAN: No, I think
it's a wonderful time.

00:51:55.900 --> 00:52:01.430
That we all are a part
of social media today

00:52:01.430 --> 00:52:05.250
and all the networks which
propagate and promote

00:52:05.250 --> 00:52:07.180
arts and culture.

00:52:07.180 --> 00:52:10.890
So I think it's
wonderful that now

00:52:10.890 --> 00:52:13.640
any musician or any
creative person--

00:52:13.640 --> 00:52:18.620
or anyone for that matter--
can post what they are doing.

00:52:18.620 --> 00:52:21.600
And I think we have
a lot of content now

00:52:21.600 --> 00:52:25.530
which is very easily available,
especially for a younger artist

00:52:25.530 --> 00:52:26.505
if he wants references.

00:52:26.505 --> 00:52:28.880
If he wants to hear
all the great masters.

00:52:28.880 --> 00:52:31.300
Everything is so
easily available.

00:52:31.300 --> 00:52:35.150
And the beautiful part is
now even most artists now

00:52:35.150 --> 00:52:39.297
