them because of this medium.

00:52:39.297 --> 00:52:40.380
So I think it's wonderful.

00:52:40.380 --> 00:52:42.610
It's great.

00:52:42.610 --> 00:52:47.030
Not many people extremely
savvy yet, but then one

00:52:47.030 --> 00:52:49.740
